OL,5,G0235 Masters: Keepers of Tradition
OL,6,     FBlacksmith: John Hogan never took
OL,7,     Fto books, but he understood metal
OL,8,     Finstinctively. When a crumbling
OL,9,     FVictorian gate at Westport House
OL,10,     Fneeded saving, there was only one
OL,11,     Fman for the job.
OL,12,G0305 Cheap European Homes
OL,13,     FCarmel from East Cork, and her
OL,14,     Fdaughter Caoimhe are finally
OL,15,     Fturning a long-held dream into
OL,16,     Freality by searching for a home in
OL,17,     FSpain's Murcia region.
